The <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhagavad_Gita" title="Bhagavad Gita">Bhagavad Gita</a> is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lord_Krishna" title="Lord Krishna" class="mw-redirect">Lord Krishna</a>'s counsel to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arjuna" title="Arjuna">Arjuna</a> on the battlefield of the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kurukshetra" title="Kurukshetra">Kurukshetra</a>.</div>
